      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEROCIOUS FRANKIE (5) showed good early dash and held on well to finish 2 lengths back over 1300m at Cranbourne. Is still well shy of her best and can use an inside barrier. Ethan Brown is a key jockey booking, and the filly has strong winning prospects. COOLY (1) resumed over this distance at Sandown-Lakeside and needed the outing. Had come off an easy Maiden win over 1500m at Caulfield-Heath and will be a lot sharper today. Maps well and has Emily Pozman's handy 2kg claim. FONDLED (4) ran a good number beaten a nose over 1200m at Ballarat, but disappointed there following, in stronger than this. The jockey gave a plausible excuse for the poor effort, and on a 6-day return, she can get back on track. JUSTDOIT (6) tries hard and will be around the mark again.",
